{"tid":1065574,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"其實買樓，只係公屋仔特別需要","createTime":"2019-03-17T11:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T20:32:07.000Z","uid":23848,"like":22,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fc80a0644bcb476bafb4c1953d5e9c10d4e64a26","tid":1065574,"uid":23848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T11:04:50.000Z","msg":"如果你父母住緊居屋/村屋/私人樓，而你又唔係特別多兄弟姊妹，你根本唔駛擔心老咗無地方住。<br />\n<br />\n先唔講到到你60歲你父母都唔係得返好多日子，你自己都會選擇返去同佢地住，順便照顧佢地；到佢地去咗你間屋就獨霸，你賣又得養老又得。<br />\n<br />\n就算你有3兄妹，到父母去咗一樣可以賣樓，每人都分幾百萬，加埋你40年儲蓄，用500萬買隻收息股都夠你住到100歲。<br />\n<br />\n根本只係得一類人重真係需要買樓&mdash;&mdash; 公屋撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038b9c4ee629885d46de5b2702cba2a897d1a324","tid":1065574,"uid":53798,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"40歲都和父母住?"},{"pid":"9a0c182e34992d7d902cfbffbcf776682b2cd58d","tid":1065574,"uid":124107,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T11:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2170fda2862c4a626d78ceff529e6c6fff13661","tid":1065574,"uid":23848,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"038b9c4ee629885d46de5b2702cba2a897d1a324","tid":1065574,"uid":53798,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"40歲都和父母住?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"每個月分部分錢儲蓄 自己租樓/做乜春住都得啦  <br />\n<br />\n人生根本唔需要浪費晌儲首期買樓供樓上，根本呢個概念要被推翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b0949e54fe83d1b49ea330be603533a822120d","tid":1065574,"uid":23848,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a0c182e34992d7d902cfbffbcf776682b2cd58d","tid":1065574,"uid":124107,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fc80a0644bcb476bafb4c1953d5e9c10d4e64a26","tid":1065574,"uid":23848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T11:04:50.000Z","msg":"如果你父母住緊居屋/村屋/私人樓，而你又唔係